Class BindingPair<F extends Feature>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MIEdge<F>

    public class BindingPair<F extends Feature>
extends AbstractMIEdge<F>
    A feature binding pair is an undirected MI edge of features that are linked to each other. By default, It will use an identityHashComparator to compare features and generate hashCodes for node A and B.
